{"id":615157,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/【立此存照】他们都是护旗手/","date":"2019-08-08T04:41:25Z","modified":"2019-08-08T04:41:25Z","title":"【立此存照】他们都是护旗手","content":"<p>近日，中共官媒陆续发起微博话题 #五星红旗有14亿护旗手 将其冲上微博热搜，据悉在转发此tag话题后，个人ID名后将会生成一个小国旗，表示自己是“14亿分之一”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18ca-iatixpm1321268.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-615158\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18ca-iatixpm1321268.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"423\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18ca-iatixpm1321268.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18ca-iatixpm1321268-300x231.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a598-iatixpm1321311.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-615159\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a598-iatixpm1321311.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"403\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a598-iatixpm1321311.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a598-iatixpm1321311-300x220.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/bf38-iatixpm1321345.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-615160\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/bf38-iatixpm1321345.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/bf38-iatixpm1321345.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/bf38-iatixpm1321345-300x235.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>香港本地也有“护旗手”出现，成为官方媒体所称的“主流声音”。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">5日晚，激进示威者来到香港尖沙咀天星码头，再次扯下五支旗杆上的国旗，并把国旗扔到海里。当晚23时20分左右，数十名来自各行各业的香港同胞前往尖沙咀“五支旗杆”，将五星红旗重新升起，用实际行动保护国旗，捍卫尊严，他们是香港护旗手！ <a href=\"https://t.co/elcOcFA6RV\">pic.twitter.com/elcOcFA6RV</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 中国观察@ChinaNNCC (@chinanncc) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/chinanncc/status/1158516984079769602?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 5, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>之后相当数量的以成龙为首的“爱国爱港”明星加入声援了此行动，表达对“大局”的坚定支持。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">香港艺人：“我们都是护旗手！” <a href=\"https://t.co/8o6saPwXK9\">pic.twitter.com/8o6saPwXK9</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 中国新闻社 (@CNS1952) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CNS1952/status/1159114949853155329?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 7, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">“五星红旗”冲上热搜·中港艺人接力当护旗手<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E6%98%9F%E6%B4%B2%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#星洲日报</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/sinchew?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#sinchew</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/y1sj3Y4VPz\">https://t.co/y1sj3Y4VPz</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/sUN2tP1k36\">pic.twitter.com/sUN2tP1k36</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Sin Chew Daily 星洲日報 (@SinChewPress) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SinChewPress/status/1158358969011724288?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 5, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>来自国内网友的护旗支持</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/huqishou.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615161\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/huqishou.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"537\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/huqishou.jpg 730w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/huqishou-300x293.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/huqishou-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>来自墙外网友网友的呛声</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">有什麼事好得過成龍做护旗手👏👏</p>\n<p>支旗好快就冧✌️ <a href=\"https://t.co/DcyZPDoniN\">pic.twitter.com/DcyZPDoniN</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Seline Chan (@chan_seline) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/chan_seline/status/1158962674463494144?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 7, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"ja\" dir=\"ltr\">成龙魔咒 <a href=\"https://t.co/vPJYjvX5Ti\">pic.twitter.com/vPJYjvX5Ti</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; SU (@sqc6241) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sqc6241/status/1124614727944925185?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 4, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">For Jackie Chen and all other China‘s patriots，which side would u save when the national flag and your lover are both drowning in the sea?<br />送给成龙大哥和各位护旗手的画<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/FreeHongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#FreeHongKong</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/antiELAB?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#antiELAB</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/bAOdNGH6wp\">pic.twitter.com/bAOdNGH6wp</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 巴丢草  Badiucao (@badiucao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1159277681084551168?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 8, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n","author":1060,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[38564,38551,9633,38693,9503,38526]}